name: PEDRO MEME
description: Pedro! The Meme coin. Embodies the Lively Spirit and Infectious Charm of Pedro. A dancing Raccoon who Grooves Through the Crypto Space with the Ease of a Street Dancer. Just as Pedro Captivates Onlookers with his Slick Moves and Spontaneous Routines. Pedro Pedro the Coin Brings a Playful and Engaging Twist to the Cryptocurrency Market.
